`market_data_latest_quotes`

The table must be a snapshot table, not an append-only history table.

Required columns:
- instrument_id (PK, FK to market_data_instruments.id)
- provider (string, nullable or non-null depending current conventions)
- provider_symbol (string, nullable or non-null depending current conventions)
- last_price (numeric)
- bid_price (numeric, nullable)
- ask_price (numeric, nullable)
- volume (numeric, nullable)
- quote_time (timestamptz, nullable)
- updated_at (timestamptz, server default now, non-null)

Constraints:
- one row per instrument only
- instrument_id is the primary key

Do not create intraday OHLC tables in this task.

